@startuml CreateClass
|Admin|
start
:1. Open class creation form;
:2. Fill in class details (name, course, schedule);
:3. Link to course;
:4. Set schedule/time;
:5. Submit form;
|ClassManagementUI|
:6. Validate class data;
|ClassController|
:7. Check if class already exists;
:8. Create new class in backend;
|Database|
:9. Save class record;
|ClassController|
:10. Return success;
|ClassManagementUI|
:11. Display confirmation;
:12. Update class list;
stop
@enduml
